2.1 Materiality assessment

2.1

Materiality assessment

– Materiality assessment based on GRI 2021 – 15 material sustainability topics of the greatest

relevance to Siemens

– Material impacts, risks, and opportunities as part of our strategic considerations

Key topics as guiding principles Our materiality assessment is based on external frameworks

like the UN Global Compact and the Standards of the Global Reporting Initiative (GRI 2021), which are the foundation for our reporting. The key topics covered in this report are struc- tured based on ESG.